"{\"uid\": \"fortune.com-2024-08-01-google-olympics-advertisement-gemini-ai-reactions\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Role: ReporterMarco Quiroz-Gutierrez is a reporter forFortunecovering general business news.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Google's Olympics-themed advertisement for its generative AI chatbot Gemini has some debating what role artificial intelligence should play in our everyday lives.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999967948043, \"rank\": 3.205189741780178e-08, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The advertisement, titled \\\"Dear Sydney,\\\" features a dad helping his daughter use Gemini to produce an AI-crafted letter to the daughter's hero, Olympic hurdler Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999984555141158, \"rank\": 1.2936835130218287e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the ad, the father asks Gemini to help create a letter \\\"telling Sydney how inspiring she is, and be sure to mention that my daughter plans on breaking her world record one day.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999984555141158, \"rank\": 1.2936835130218287e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She says sorry, not sorry.)\\\"\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, the ad drew backlash from some worried about AI's role in such an emotional and personal task as writing a fan letter.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several called the message\\\"tone deaf\\\"and accused it of promoting laziness to create a letter devoid of meaning.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having a child use Gemini to write a one-time letter, that is supposed to be thoughtful, where spelling and grammar mistakes would have surely been forgiven, is just plain dumb.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I find myself judging the dad hard lol,\\\" one user wrote on the subredditr/CommercialsIHate.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others online said the advertisement, like others promoting Gemini, signaled that tech companies want people to think less and off-load creative thinking or social interactions to machines.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One such example criticized on Reddit included a Gemini commercial from May that, among other examples, showed a girl asking the chatbot what to say to her friends while they weresitting in front of her.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reddit\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shelly Palmer, a media professor at Syracuse University,wrotein a blog post that the father in the ad was acting irresponsibly.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly Palmer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly_Palmer\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\", \"score\": 0.999999287571226, \"rank\": 3.047303280923638e-07, \"text\": \"Syracuse University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syracuse_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The father in the video is not encouraging his daughter to learn to express herself.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of guiding her to use her own words and communicate authentically, he is teaching her to rely on AI for this critical human skill,\\\" Palmer wrote.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to a request for comment, a Google spokesperson said the ad was meant to show how Gemini can provide a starting point or draft to help with the writing process.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999967948043, \"rank\": 3.205189741780178e-08, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.962078631991378, \"rank\": 0.0394160796714218, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe that AI can be a great tool for enhancing human creativity, but can never replace it,\\\" the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999331521, \"rank\": 6.415394805263629e-11, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the online criticism, the \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" commercial is one of the better performing Olympic advertisements, according to data from ad testing firm System1, cited byBusiness Insider.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The firm gave the ad a 4.4 out of 5.9 (a score it described as \\\"strong\\\") on its scale of how much the commercial could create long-term growth for the brand.\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ad had more than 300,000 views onYouTubeas of Thursday.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It follows a coherent story, focuses on characters with agency and vitality, and prioritizes people over the product,\\\" System1 chief customer officer Jon Evans told BI.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2803, \"end\": 2812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Evans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jon Evans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 2818, \"end\": 2820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2819535257359775e-19, \"text\": \"BI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Business_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Additionally, it champions diversity and inclusion by highlighting women in sports, providing young girls with role models.\\\"\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Fortune Media IP Limited.\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"score\": 0.9999999956735337, \"rank\": 4.326563965004431e-09, \"text\": \"Fortune\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\"}, {\"begin\": 2972, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"score\": 0.9999999540668807, \"rank\": 4.593282584831791e-08, \"text\": \"IP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use of this site constitutes acceptance of ourTerms of UseandPrivacy Policy|CA Notice at Collection and Privacy Notice|Do Not Sell/Share My Personal InformationFORTUNE is a trademark of Fortune Media IP Limited, registered in the U.S. and other countries.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"score\": 0.9999999956735337, \"rank\": 4.326563965004431e-09, \"text\": \"Fortune\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\"}, {\"begin\": 3205, \"end\": 3207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"score\": 0.9999999540668807, \"rank\": 4.593282584831791e-08, \"text\": \"IP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia